summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Engineer to incur an indebtedness against the General Fund of The City of Seattle in the sum of $580.95 on account of the cost and expense of the construction of a bulkhead in front of lots 2, 3, 4, 5, block 1, and lots 1 and 2, block 2, Replat of Green Lake Home Addition, as authorized by Ordinance No. 22819.
